zh_CN.DialogText: 两个不怎么熟悉的人站在门口

en_US.DialogText: Two unfamiliar people stood at the door

zh_CN.DialogText: 请问你们有什么事吗？

en_US.DialogText: What can I do for you?

zh_CN.DialogText: 在末日时代，两陌生人一起造访可能是眸中危险的信号，因此门后就藏了一把刀。

en_US.DialogText: In the apocalyptic era, two strangers visiting together may be a sign of danger in the eyes, so there is a knife hidden behind the door.

zh_CN.DialogText: 别紧张，这个...我们是来邀请你加入公社的，老工人建议我们找你来当这个公社工程师的职位

en_US.DialogText: Relax, this We are here to invite you to join the commune. The old worker suggested that we find you as an engineer in the commune

zh_CN.DialogText: 什么？你在说些什么啊？

en_US.DialogText: what? What are you talking about?

zh_CN.DialogText: 就是让你来公社当工程师，我们所有人共享收集到的食物材料，以及每个人的技能。

en_US.DialogText: Let you be an engineer in the commune. We all share the collected food materials and everyone's skills.

zh_CN.DialogText: 没想到，那个老工人真的搞成了啊，不过，我也不知道这能持续多久...

en_US.DialogText: Unexpectedly, the old worker really made it, but I don't know how long it will last

zh_CN.DialogText: 所以，你的第一个工作就是帮助这边这位孩子

en_US.DialogText: So your first job is to help the child here

zh_CN.DialogText: 嗯？

en_US.DialogText: Huh？

zh_CN.DialogText: 啊哈哈，你好啊....

en_US.DialogText: Ah ha ha, Hello....

zh_CN.DialogText: 抱歉，我有点社恐

en_US.DialogText: Sorry, I'm a little social phobia

zh_CN.DialogText: 什么时候了还社恐？有事就说，有屁就放。

en_US.DialogText: When is it time for social fear? Just say what are you doing here.

zh_CN.DialogText: 我知道大家都很困难，但是呢，怎么说呢....

en_US.DialogText: know it's hard for everyone，But what am I going to say.....

zh_CN.DialogText: 我真想给你一拳

en_US.DialogText: I really want to punch you

zh_CN.DialogText: 噗嗤，啊，抱歉你们继续

en_US.DialogText: He laughed in spite ofhimself ‘ah, sorry, you go on’

zh_CN.DialogText: 啊，抱歉抱歉，我是听我邻居说的，我的小屋子是用铁皮搭的，最近有点晃动了，所以...

en_US.DialogText: Ah, sorry, sorry, I heard from my neighbor. My little house is made of iron sheet. It's shaking a little recently, so...

zh_CN.DialogText: 别让我猜你想说什么，你是想让我帮你修理你的小棚子吧？

en_US.DialogText: Don't let me guess what you're trying to say. Do you want me to help you repair your shed?

zh_CN.DialogText: 没办法啊，我是从商场地下车库来的，到的时候就只剩下站厅可以住了

en_US.DialogText: I can't help it. I came from the underground garage of the commercial centre. When I arrived, there was only the station hall to live in

zh_CN.DialogText: 我没问你这个，算了算了，我想应该给不了我什么报酬吧？

en_US.DialogText: I didn't ask you this. Forget it. I don't think you can give me any reward?

zh_CN.DialogText: 啊，这个啊，你以后可以从公社领取食物和申请某些高级材料，这也算报酬吧

en_US.DialogText: Ah, well, you can get food from the commune and apply for some advanced materials in the future. This is also a reward

zh_CN.DialogText: 只有不知道能否兑现的承诺吗？让我想想....

en_US.DialogText: Is there only a promise that you don't know whether you can keep it? Let me see....
